{"tid":146691,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［丁屋］今時今日，買村花既風險有幾大?","createTime":"2017-03-07T10:10:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T15:01:10.000Z","uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1c66d828521b668f4524388698f8a1b28fc0881","tid":146691,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"講緊先買地，再同個丁夾申請起丁屋，起完之後歸你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有個朋友話６－７百萬包哂所有野，見佢咁撚大膽，想知風險有幾高？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除左個丁可以玩野，下屆特首一玩野你等緊地政審批都凍過水？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55881b8f83c32b9b3fec3d205923c5f70778a9a2","tid":146691,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:14:51.000Z","msg":"有無人識　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d045733c8443312aa76163ce429dbb04e01735a","tid":146691,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:18:34.000Z","msg":"唔識，幫你呼喚原居民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf446b99ffa0f0411f3a3e7cff7c8d0ff4c81413","tid":146691,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:25:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔識，幫你呼喚原居民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ae87aa8c1abc561f65fd3e6351aa2882523f70","tid":146691,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T11:27:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔識，幫你呼喚原居民 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.menclub.