,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:52:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df478e8613551d9af021eafe3406549759a7755","tid":146691,"uid":54951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T15:58:25.000Z","msg":"咪姐係套丁？"},{"pid":"a9df1a8e0358ef6ca01067ef30e323d39763fd0f","tid":146691,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪姐係套丁？</blockquote><br />\n我就係咁話佢<br />\n但佢話係有風險但搏得過"},{"pid":"a8221c27fb7051e185f3db9b3a267b15a2640af2","tid":146691,"uid":54951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咪姐係套丁？</blockquote><br />\n我就係咁話佢<br />\n但佢話係有風險但搏得過</blockquote><br />\n私底下同丁簽個份約又擺唔到上大枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af866e93e2402941602efc576aba2773b448284f","tid":146691,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T10:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咪姐係套丁？</blockquote><br />\n我就係咁話佢<br />\n但佢話係有風險但搏得過</blockquote><br />\n私底下同丁簽個份約又擺唔到上大枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽過有d仆街丁會用就就破產做借口<br />\n定期借d椅叫你比幾萬佢應急 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e58572733f74d2193b2664d2c52b2e847d8000","tid":146691,"uid":22876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:12:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b985d303e367144c9f0506d134d02ab9b2e855","tid":146691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T20:09:04.000Z","msg":"香港啲地係唔賣俾人嘅, 你住緊塊地只係香港政府租俾你 <br />\n<br />\n除咗 999 年期嘅地契, 其他地契多數係 50 年嘅, 由 1997 年計起, 呢類 50 年期地契會係 2047 年 expire, 唔關你係唔係丁權丁屋 or 補地價事 <br />\n<br />\n地契 expire 之後, 香港政府可以選擇同你續租 (佢會要求你俾續租嘅租金, 可以係 $1, 亦可以係 $1B), 香港政府亦有權點都唔同你續收返你塊地 (拆你間屋趕你走乜都唔賠俾你都得) <br />\n<br />\n大廈住得人多, 通常地契到期政府唔會攪事激起民憤, 通常會用 $1/year 續租俾你, 丁屋喇喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e325c53305c18a60e344ae8dc2a7dfc2b75936a","tid":146691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"300/350個d多數係'湯'出黎，又或者幾原有700既拆左再起一梯兩伙既300/350,我有個行家都做過三間呢d,點解咁做？租得/賣得好價d, 呢家好多3-400呎單位賣140-180萬，d人見到1字頭覺得好低，實際係新界區買個700呎中層都係200-230萬左右(當中有d係全新),仲有大把可以揀"},{"pid":"f444ff5f427924e0944726e94e729c6a2b8f22f6","tid":146691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:19:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b957c0215b6e87b20ad0a8e3e9431265f7baa5f5","tid":146691,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3246b1bf47751c0edd8b1629326fab6e6484b888","tid":146691,"uid":5413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"違法合約好似冇法律效力<br />\n<br />\n新特首上場可能捉套丁"}]}